column5: I've been hearing how the shot is good and Bad.  Anyone have any input.  Also this Video Scared me off from the flu shot
Lock down in 10,9,8,7,6,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,  Think we had this one bud. Got the lock and they threw away the key.

As a parent this has been  huge question for me and my wife, and I can not take a chance with giving my kids a shot that has had minimal tsting and that we do not know what the side effects could or will be down the road.  So I have drawn a hard line and NO WAY will we do it.  FLEX
